So, that being said, if you fit this profile, and are looking for someone like me, we have a very good start to an incredible relationship, that may become the stuff of movies. Maybe not the movie stuff, but, the odds are stacked in our favor; so,

how adventurous are you?

I prefer to meet in person, rather than to go through email changes leading to nothing. Respond to this post, with a conversation, rather than a one line, "Hit me up!" type of message. Use an original subject line that represents your individuality, and you'll get my attention. Start a deep, interesting conversation that we may continue in person, and you may get my phone number. Meet up with me, and you may get more.




Zero intimate attraction toward males here, so men, don't waste your time trying to connect with me.
Not into HWP, thick, or BBW women as intimacy partners.
Zero tolerance for any kind of abusive behavior; if I perceive it as a pattern, I will leave you. 

